{"word":"κατακόπτω","slug":"κατακόπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατακόπτω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to cut down, cut in pieces, cut up</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor2 <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>κατακοπείς</el> <i>cut in pieces</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to kill, slay</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b>in a military sense, <i>to cut in pieces, \"cut up, \"</i> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>; <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor2 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>κατακοπῆναι</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b>generally, <i>to break in pieces, destroy</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to coin into money</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}